race.comment: INTRIGUING STATE (7) won his Maiden first-up and has placed the three outings since. Draws inside today and Stockdale stays aboard. He's been kept on the fresh side and this is a suitable assignment. BRASH LASS (14) also presents at peak fitness. Followed the Maiden win with two close-up efforts at Warrnambool, where she led. Has an inside gate and the free-running filly will take plenty of catching. AUCKLAND (6) will need luck from a tough gate but he keeps winning and deserves plenty of consideration on an 8-day return. ZEMGRINDA (4) resumes and is proven fresh. Will need some luck in the run but he'd be in the finish at best.
